Entry.JapaneseText: モクラド村か……オスミナ山地の向こうに村が あるとは、今までに聞いた事はないが……
Entry.EnglishText: Mocrado Village... I've never heard of a village on the other side of the Osmina Mountains until now...

Entry.JapaneseText: <Eugene>が知らないってコトは、 よっぽど人に知られてない村なんだネ。
Entry.EnglishText: Well if you weren't aware of it, then most people must not know about it either.

Entry.JapaneseText: 少なくとも、地図には 描かれていない村だな。
Entry.EnglishText: At the very least, it's not shown on the map.

Entry.JapaneseText: 新しい村？ あ、でも、十年前には あったんだもんね……
Entry.EnglishText: Was it founded recently? Ah, but he said that it was there ten years ago...

Entry.JapaneseText: ……行って、確かめるしかないな……
Entry.EnglishText: ...We'll just have to go and see for ourselves...
